<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Welcome to CitizenConnect360</title>
    <style>
        * {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            box-sizing: border-box;
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
        }
        body {
            background-color: #f4f4f4;
            padding: 20px;
        }
        .container {
            width: 100%;
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: auto;
            background-color: #ffffff;
            border-radius: 10px;
            overflow: hidden;
            box-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        }
        .header {
            background-color: green;
            color: white;
            text-align: center;
            padding: 20px;
        }
        .header p {
            font-size: 45px;
            font-weight: bold;
        }
        .content {
            padding: 20px;
        }
        .content img {
            width: 100%;
            height: auto;
            border-radius: 10px;
        }
        .content p {
            color: #333333;
            font-size: 18px;
            margin: 10px 0;
        }
        .content h2 {
            font-size: 35px;
            color: #333333;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }
        .content .welcome-text {
            font-size: 30px;
            color: #666666;
            margin: 10px 0;
        }
        .content .details {
            font-size: 20px;
            color: #666666;
            margin: 10px 0;
        }
        .footer {
            background-color: green;
            color: white;
            text-align: center;
            padding: 20px;
        }
        .footer a {
            color: #ffffff;
            text-decoration: none;
            background-color: green;
            padding: 10px 20px;
            border-radius: 5px;
            font-size: 18px;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="header">
            <p>CitizenConnect360</p>
        </div>
        <div class="content">
            <img src="https://cdn.gencraft.com/prod/user/09428aa0-8f76-4c30-9337-bf2363f2eb6d/e34e8866-7814-4253-bb40-ba56ce12e8e4/image/image0_0.jpg?Expires=1721810640&Signature=i8Q00u17ZrHiEWDwzPAkcdDEDmEywf73zWBdLyf3POvrf5NpyAgcQeAjNdRKhMWII6GrdS0jYKKW7eiTebICHod4nFgst-dtWU2hnqkOYIQCifwgBlK3NvqTC9YzfCWAsl8cgLShBlP6YqwfMVBuJ3~bu2vU7vwTsq0PlA7zfvXSijJG5xd9-eBa3B57wayB9aLqHBwZv1qjWuMgKddA-VNPw8u5bq~BZgiRyzJJMKuo9ZZ6IPZRx37aerxNt0z7feRf6ZCvZ~EjhB45pzxPCT0Gfwg3Gu3oNHbS4pytq1ZgM6gpK-hcV5Tc81KDyz3aPB9WpeF9d0jPzaXly0mKkQ__&Key-Pair-Id=K3RDDB1TZ8BHT8" alt="image"/>
            <p>Hello <%=name%>,</p>
            <h2>Welcome to CitizenConnect360</h2>
            <p class="welcome-text">Empowering Citizens for a Better Future</p>
            <p class="details">
                CitizenConnect360 is dedicated to bridging the gap between citizens and government by providing a platform for understanding crucial government documents like the Finance Bill, encouraging informed participation and advocacy.<br>
                Our platform enables citizens to express views, engage in decision-making, and efficiently report incidents during emergencies.<br>
                Join us in making a difference!
